      "y": 733,
      "width": 830,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A can do a work in 10 days and B in 15 days. A works for 4\ndays and B works for 9 days to complete the work. If the\ntotal wage is Rs.3000, what is each person's share?",
      "fontSize": 13,
