      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A does 8/20 work in 8 days\nStep 2: B does remaining 12/20\nStep 3: Ratio = 8:12 = 2:3\n  B = 4000x3/5 = Rs.2400\n\n  Work: |████ A=8/20 ████|██████ B=12/20 ██████|\n  Days:   8 days A          9 days B\n  Pay:    Rs.1600           Rs.2400\n\nTRICK:\nWages by work done (not time!)\nA:B = 8:12 = 2:3\n1 part = 4000/5 = 800\nA=1600, B=2400\n\nAnswer: B gets Rs.2400 ✓",
