    {
      "id": "el_48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1603,
      "width": 816,
      "height": 65,
      "text": "A worker is paid Rs.15 for each finished item and Rs.5 is\ndeducted for each rejected item. In a day he produces 50\nitems, out of which 8 are rejected. What is his daily\nearning?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 48,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A worker is paid Rs.15 for each finished item and Rs.5 is\ndeducted for each rejected item. In a day he produces 50\nitems, out of which 8 are rejected. What is his daily\nearning?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_49",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1678,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4900,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 49,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1700,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Accepted = 50-8 = 42\nStep 2: Earned = 42x15 = Rs.630\n        Deducted = 8x5 = Rs.40\nStep 3: Net = 630-40 = Rs.590\n\n  50 items produced\n  |████ 42 accepted ████|██ 8 rejected ██|\n  42 × Rs.15 = +630\n   8 × Rs.5  =  -40\n  Net = Rs.590\n\nTRICK:\nNet = (Accepted x rate) - (Rejected x penalty)\n= 42x15 - 8x5 = 630-40 = Rs.590\nEach rejected costs 15+5=20 vs accepted\n\nAnswer: Rs.590 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 50,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Accepted = 50-8 = 42\nStep 2: Earned = 42x15 = Rs.630\n        Deducted = 8x5 = Rs.40\nStep 3: Net = 630-40 = Rs.590\n\n  50 items produced\n  |████ 42 accepted ████|██ 8 rejected ██|\n  42 × Rs.15 = +630\n   8 × Rs.5  =  -40\n  Net = Rs.590\n\nTRICK:\nNet = (Accepted x rate) - (Rejected x penalty)\n= 42x15 - 8x5 = 630-40 = Rs.590\nEach rejected costs 15+5=20 vs accepted\n\nAnswer: Rs.590 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
